high_descs: Turn right and face the counter by the stove in front of you.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter on your left.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the microwave on your left.
Place the knife in the microwave in front of you.
Turn left then face the cabinet above the counter on your right.
Take a tomato slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the microwave on your left.
Place the tomato slice inside the microwave, heat it up and take it out.
Turn right then face the table on your right.
Place the tomato slice on the table in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Move to the area of the counter to the right of the range.
Pick up the knife with the gold colored handle.
Turn left, move past the range, then turn left and move to the area of the counter to the left of the red microwave.
Slice the tomato between the knife and the red microwave on the counter using the knife.
Move to the right and face the red microwave.
Open the microwave, place the knife on the plate in the microwave, and then close the microwave door.
Move to the left and face the area of the counter to the left of the red microwave.
Pick up a tomato slice by the rear of the dispenser bottle from the counter.
Move to the right and face the red microwave.
Open the microwave, place the tomato slice to the rear of the knife on the plate, microwave the tomato slice, then open the microwave, pick up the tomato slice, and then close the microwave door.
Turn right and move toward the brown door then turn right and move to the table in the corner of the room.
Place the tomato slice on the table between the spoon and the edge of the table closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn right then then to the counter on the right
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left head to the counter with tomato beside the microwave
Slice the tomato on the counter
Turn right then face the microwave
Open the microwave put in the knife then close the microwave
Turn left then face the tomato on the counter
Pick up a slice tomato
Turn right then face the microwave
Open the microwave put in and out the slice tomato then close the microwave
Turn right then head to the table
Put the slice tomato on the edge of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice tomato on the edge of the table
